2007-11-01  Ryan Lortie  <desrt@desrt.ca>

	* gappinfo.c (g_app_info_launch, g_app_info_launch_uris):
	* gappinfo.h (g_app_info_launch, g_app_info_launch_uris):
	* gwin32appinfo.c (g_win32_app_info_launch):
